---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    fontSize: 16px
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    state "start" as nStart
    state "question" as nQuestion
    state "free_talk" as nFreeTalk
    state "__confirm_exit__" as nConfirm
    state "end" as nEnd
    state "verificação final" as nFinalCheck
    state "consolidação" as nConsolidate

    [*] --> nStart

    nStart --> nQuestion: primeiro nó do roteiro
    nStart --> nFreeTalk: primeiro nó do roteiro

    nQuestion --> nQuestion: aresta condicional (edge_id)<br/>ou aresta padrão (edge_id = "")
    nQuestion --> nFreeTalk: transição do roteiro
    nQuestion --> nEnd: transição do roteiro

    nFreeTalk --> nFreeTalk: continue (zera streak)<br/>reengage (incrementa streak)
    nFreeTalk --> nConfirm: ask_to_end<br/>(streak atinge threshold = 2)
    nFreeTalk --> nEnd: exit (closeFreeTalk)

    nConfirm --> nFreeTalk: aluno quer continuar
    nConfirm --> nEnd: aluno confirma saída

    nEnd --> nFinalCheck: oferece complementar
    nFinalCheck --> nConsolidate
    nConsolidate --> [*]: dispara análise reflexiva (assíncrona)

    note right of nQuestion
        Resolução via NextNodeResolver. Em nós
        question, o BranchClassifier escolhe a
        aresta a partir da resposta do aluno.
    end note

    note right of nConfirm
        Nó sentinela __confirm_exit__,
        criado em runtime (não existe no grafo).
    end note
